title: Bobby Announces Million Dollar Show Lineup + Bobby Honors Reba McEntire At Kennedy Center Honors Event
itunes:title: Bobby Announces Million Dollar Show Lineup + Bobby Honors Reba McEntire At Kennedy Center Honors Event
description:
Bobby announces the lineup for this year's Million Dollar Show. Bobby gives the highlights from honoring Reba at the Kennedy Center Honors. Also, Tucker Beathard stops by to talk about his new album "Nobody's Everything."
